oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Songwriter Soiree Rivers at Rutherford Oxford Square
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Rutherford, River; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (light blue, navy, and red on white) announcing the Ole Miss Women's Council Songwriter Soiree with Rivers Rutherford and others at the Oxford Square on October 13. Poster features woodcuts of music notes and a rose.
